us]]<ref name=\"Bode\"/><ref>J. Ansorge. 2003. Insects from the Lower Toarcian of middle Europe and England. Acta Zoologica Cracoviensia 46(Suppl):291-310</ref>\n|\n*''Necrotaulius parvulus''\n|\n* Holzmaden\n* Niedersachsen\n* Kerkhofen\n* Hattorf, Fallersleben\n|\nSpecimens\n|\nA [[Caddisfly]].\n|\n|-\n|\n[[Prohemerobius]]<ref name=\"Bode\"/><ref>A. G. Ponomarenko. 1995. Upper Liassic neuropterans (Insecta) from Lower Saxony, Germany. Russian Entomological Journal 4(1-4):73-89</ref>\n|\n*''Prohemerobius prodromus''\n*''Prohemerobius septemvirgatus''\n*''Prohemerobius mediolatus ''\n|\n* Niedersachsen\n|\nSpecimens\n|\nA [[Lacewing]] of the family [[Prohemerobiidae]].\n|\n|-\n|\n[[Parhemerobius]]<ref name=\"Bode\"/>\n|\n*''Parhemerobius dilatatus''\n*''Parhemerobius bodei''\n|\n* Niedersachsen\n|\nSpecimens\n|\nA [[Lacewing]] of the family [[Prohemerobiidae]].\n|\n|-\n|\n[[Paractinophlebia]]<ref name=\"Bode\"/>\n|\n*''Paractinophlebia grasselensis''\n|\n* Niedersachsen\n|\nSpecimens\n|\nA [[Lacewing]] of the family [[Prohemerobiidae]].\n|\n|-\n|\n[[Liassopsychops]]<ref name=\"Bode\"/>\n|\n*''Liassopsychops curvata''\n|\n* Niedersachsen\n|\nSpecimens\n|\nA [[Lacewing]] of the family [[Prohemerobiidae]].\n|\n|-\n|\n[[Tetanoptilon]]<ref name=\"Bode\"/>\n|\n*''Tetanoptilon brunsvicense ''\n|\n* Niedersachsen\n|\nSpecimens\n|\nA lance [[Lacewing]] of the family [[Osmylidae]].\n|\n|-\n|\n[[Liassocicada]]<ref name=\"Bode\"/><ref>A. Nel. 1996. Un Tettigarctidae fossile du Lias europ\u00e9en (Cicadomorpha, Cicadoidea, Tettigarctidae). \u00c9cole Pratique des Hautes \u00c9tudes, Biologie et \u00c9volution des Insectes 9:83-94</ref>\n|\n*''Liassocicada mueckei'' \n*''Liassocicada antecedens''\n|\n* Rhine-Danube canal, Km 112\n* Beienrode\n|\nSpecimens\n|\nA [[Hairy Cicada]] of the family [[Tettigarctidae]]. \n|\n|-\n|\n[[Thilopterus]]<ref name=\"Bode\"/>\n|\n*''Thilopterus lampei''\n|\n* Schandelah\n|\nSpecimens\n|\nA [[Wasp]] of the family [[Ephialtitidae]]. \n|\n|-\n|\n[[Symphytopterus]]<ref name=\"Bode\"/>\n|\n*''Symphytopterus liasinus''\n|\n* Niedersachsen\n|\nSpecimens\n|\nA [[Wasp]] of the family [[Ephialtitidae]].\n|\n|-\n|\n[[Liadobracona]]<ref name=\"Bode\"/>\n|\n*''Liadobracona raduhna''\n|\n* Niedersachsen\n|\nSpecimens\n|\nA [[Wasp]] of the family [[Ephialtitidae]].\n|\n|-\n|\n[[Agmatozoon]]<ref name=\"Bode\"/>\n|\n*''Agmatozoon articulatum '' \n|\n* Niedersachsen\n|\nSpecimens\n|\nA non classified [[Insect]].\n|\n|-\n|\n[[Campeulites]]<ref name=\"Bode\"/>\n|\n*''Campeulites cylindricus'' \n|\n* Niedersachsen\n|\nSpecimens\n|\nA non classified [[Insect]].\n|\n|-\n|\n[[Tomeferusa]]<ref name=\"Bode\"/>\n|\n*''Tomeferusa abdita'' \n|\n* Niedersachsen\n|\nSpecimens\n|\nA non classified [[Insect]].\n|\n|-\n|\n[[Trimerocephalium]]<ref name=\"Bode\"/>\n|\n*''Trimerocephalium incisum'' \n|\n* Niedersachsen\n|\nSpecimens\n|\nA non classified [[Insect]].\n|\n|-\n|\n[[Elasmoscolex]]<ref name=\"Bode\"/>\n|\n*''Elasmoscolex hamatus '' \n|\n* Niedersachsen\n|\nSpecimens\n|\nA non classified [[Insect]].\n|\n|-\n|\n[[Epimetrophora]]<ref name=\"Bode\"/>\n|\n*''Epimetrophora recta'' \n|\n* Niedersachsen\n|\nSpecimens\n|\nA non classified [[Insect]].\n|\n|-\n|\n[[Oocephalina]]<ref name=\"Bode\"/>\n|\n*''Oocephalina mutilata'' \n|\n* Niedersachsen\n|\nSpecimens\n|\nA non classified [[Insect]].\n|\n|-\n|\n[[Platycorion]]<ref name=\"Bode\"/>\n|\n*''Platycorion utroquelaesum'' \n|\n* Niedersachsen\n|\nSpecimens\n|\nA non classified [[Insect]].\n|\n|-\n|\n[[Protomyrmeleon]]<ref name=\"Bode\"/>\n|\n*''Protomyrmeleon grasselensis'' \n|\n* Niedersachsen\n|\nSpecimens\n|\nA [[Dicondylia]]n, from the family [[Protomyrmeleontidae]].\n|\n|-\n|\n[[Dorniella]]<ref name=\"Bode\"/>\n|\n*''Dorniella pulchra'' \n|\n* Beienrode\n|\nSpecimens\n|\nA basal [[Insect]] of the family [[Blattogryllidae]].\n|\n|-\n|\n[[Geinitzia]]<ref name=\"Bode\"/><ref>A. Bode. 1905. Orthoptera and Neuroptera from the Upper Lias of Braunschweig. Yearbook of the Royal Prussian State G